FLAC-Convert                             Originally created by nijet99@gmail.com
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
FLAC-Optimizer is a simple bash script that optimizes flac files.


Features:
 - Set compression level
 - Set tags to be removes
 - Chose whether to remove embedded art
 - Chose what other file types should be "saved" like cue and log files
 
 
Usage:
 - Customize your settings at the top of the script
 - Run the script
 - Advice: Run it first on a test collection and set a test destination and verify
           if everything is to your liking

 
Requirements:
 - flac
 
 
Known issues:
 - None
